data.description: 4 bed, 2.5 bath ranch home on almost 1 Acre. 2 car attached garage with an additional 1.5 car detached garage. 2 driveways. A huge deck for entertaining with a built in screen room & a small deck for relaxing. Large living room with natural fireplace. First floor laundry. Basement has 3 finished rooms currently used as an office, rec room & workout room. There is also an unfinished workshop area. Exterior drain tile in the yard that keeps the basement dry. Included are refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, washer, dryer, riding lawnmower with attachments, pool table, universal workout machine, cardio rider, speed bag, stereo equipment & speakers in basement, dehumidifier, desks in basement bonus room. Sewer is connected to Racine sewage district. Dining room currently being used as living room
